TITLE

*Set the defaults for precision simulations
DEFAULTS                                                              PRECISIO
*Define the beam characteristics
BEAM
*Define the beam position
BEAMPOS
GEOBEGIN                                                              COMBNAME
    0    0          
BOX BLCKHOLE   -250.0 250.0 -250.0 0 0 500.0 500.0 0 0 0 -500.0 0
BOX OUTER      -50.0 50.0 -50.0 0 0 100.0 100.0 0 0 0 -100.0 0
BOX TARGET     -5.0 5.0 -5.0 0 0 10.0 10.0 0 0 0 -10.0 0
END
BLCKHOLE     5 +BLCKHOLE -OUTER
OUTER1       5 +OUTER -TARGET
TARGET       5 +TARGET
END
GEOEND
*..+....1....+....2....+....3....+....4....+....5....+....6....+....7..
*Set the random number seed
RANDOMIZ         1.0
ASSIGNMA    BLCKHOLE  BLCKHOLE
ASSIGNMA      VACUUM    OUTER1
ASSIGNMA    MAGNESIU    TARGET
*Set the number of primary histories to be simulated in the run
START
STOP
